Package Controller

Class InfoWindowManager

java.lang.Object
Controller.InfoWindowManager
public class InfoWindowManager extends Object
This class is responsible for the info window manager. It contains the methods for listing files in the transcripts panel, showing text in the view panel and showing stats in the stats panel.
